summary: This appears to be a screenshot or system interface from a Hewlett-Packard computer's BIOS/UEFI setup utility showing the date and time settings. The document shows the system date was set to August 21, 2019, which is shortly after Jeffrey Epstein's death in custody on August 10, 2019.

events.title: Computer System Date Setting
events.description: A Hewlett-Packard computer system shows its date set to August 21, 2019 in the BIOS/UEFI setup utility

keyFacts: The document shows a computer system interface with date set to August 21, 2019
This date is 11 days after Jeffrey Epstein's death in custody on August 10, 2019
The document appears to be from a Hewlett-Packard computer's BIOS/UEFI setup utility
The interface shows options for storage, security, power, and system information settings
